{"tid":603274,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[誠請大家入來]坐的士差啲死 以後唔坐","createTime":"2018-03-23T15:08:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T17:23:07.000Z","uid":148317,"like":15,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"f60890ba8a18dcb7e37cce1dfb9cec2dd174429a","tid":603274,"uid":148317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T15:08:11.000Z","msg":"小弟今日朝早10左右為左唔遲到，而坐的士翻學。（$29.1車程）<br />\n我一直都好好態度，上車已經有講唔刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  跟著佢聽到個目的地（可能近）DC9就開始西口西面，一直自言自語，我帶住耳機聽唔清楚佢講咩，隱約地聽到 咁撚西，個刻我有d驚。然後起燈位，個時佢大大力打對車門同開窗大叫，仲見到佢怒視我，個刻我感受到生命有威脅，一直都唔敢出聲。 然後到下一個燈位，佢突然急停，又再怒視我。就到目的地，我已要求早落，佢好彩肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我比錢個時，佢一直鬧我，我一直say sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我落左車之後，我有回頭望個DC9，仲見到佢怒視我。<br />\n我想講坐短途車就一定要受氣？坐的士根本就係一件比錢買難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  以後我寧願遲到都唔撚再坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想問個的士狗咁樣嘅行為有無得告？我依家仲驚緊 <br />\n如果各位Ching 遇到依啲問題會點處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b5f36627a997048c9601bba1b5062780b39f597","tid":603274,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T15:10:00.000Z","msg":"落車，抄低車牌同名，投訴"},{"pid":"dbd10755478add226fca39c5d8a8b8f579ad196c","tid":603274,"uid":113178,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T15:10:23.000Z","msg":"Call uber <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba4bdc7cbefd5d08f7ef6ffd86b0bdaa85f0b242","tid":603274,"uid":148317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T15:10:34.000Z","msg":"希望各位可以幫忙宣傳出去，避免再發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e36bf0876a3780b3ee063cb20ddd600129b4d52c","tid":603274,"uid":147330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T15:11:26.000Z","msg":"點解唔拎部手機錄佢呢？<img src=\"/asset